invariant io_extra217.buffwriter_no_read1:
  description: "io.BufferedWriter.__dict__.__contains__('read1') == False — read1 is NOT present on BufferedWriter; it is a read-only method absent from write-only buffered streams; confirmed Python 3.14.3 macOS"
